title: First Printed Title
text_content:
Titles are printed for vehicles at no fee when the owner
previously elected to not receive a printed title and
and then requests a printed title.
To obtain a printed title:
Order online
OR
Bring your current registration card and your driver's license or ID card to your local
customer service center.
If your vehicle is free of liens, you will receive an original title for your vehicle.
NOTE
:
If a title has been printed for any reason after DMV has been requested to hold the title, subsequent requests for a printed title will be done as a
replacement title
or
substitute title
and the appropriate fee will be charged.
